Mark: What happens now?
if {selected_character} == "celestine":
	Celestine: Victor has a chance to change. To learn why he was really hurting.
	Celestine: His father's expectations. His need to be the best. His loneliness.
	Celestine: Whether he takes that chance is up to him.
	Mark: You think he will?
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s5/Conrad looks toward the door Victor walked through..mp3" volume=0 bus="Master"]
	Celestine looks toward the door where Victor left.
	Celestine: I think he wants to. And sometimes, that's enough to start.
